##################
# Autotest HowTo #
##################

1. How to run test instance

cp data/meris/TEMPLATE_template.map conf/template.map
cp ../eoxserver/conf/TEMPLATE_eoxserver.conf conf/eoxserver.conf

cd <path_to_eoxserver_directory>
python manage.py loaddata data/fixtures/some_fixture.json ...
python manage.py runserver

# To load all fixtures type:
python manage.py loaddata auth_data.json initial_rangetypes.json testing_base.json testing_coverages.json


2. How to update fixtures

Run

cd <path_to_eoxserver_directory>
python manage.py dumpdata --format=json --indent=4 > tmp.json
Inspect file e.g. with: meld tmp.json server/fixtures/initial_data.json
mv tmp.json server/fixtures/initial_data.json

3. How to run unittests

# services only
python manage.py test services

# for all modules
python manage.py test services coverages backends core

# or simply
python manage.py test
# this will also make some django tests.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
